FROM rust:1.60.0-slim-buster AS build
WORKDIR /usr/src
RUN apt update && apt install --no-install-recommends build-essential g++ pkg-config musl musl-tools -y
RUN rustup target add x86_64-unknown-linux-musl
RUN USER=root cargo new mitsuba
WORKDIR /usr/src/mitsuba
COPY Cargo.toml Cargo.lock ./
RUN cargo build --release

COPY static ./static
COPY migrations ./migrations
COPY sqlx-data.json ./sqlx-data.json
COPY src ./src

ENV SQLX_OFFLINE="true"
RUN cargo install --target x86_64-unknown-linux-musl --path .

FROM alpine:3.13.4
COPY --from=build /usr/local/cargo/bin/mitsuba .
RUN mkdir /data
VOLUME /data
CMD ["./mitsuba start"]
